					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>A burger so good, you'll be dead before you eat it!</em></p> <blockquote> <p>the only item is &quot;dado borger&quot; listed enough times to cover the entire menu.</p> </blockquote> <p>If I hadn't already lost it at &quot;dado c. dado&quot;, this would have clinched the upvote.</p> <p>I already trust dado.</p> <blockquote> <p>dado encounter technical difficulty due to large amount of bird</p> </blockquote> <p>I&#8230; <em>geez what even</em>. Is this the end of dado?</p> <blockquote> <p>A Glock-20 pistol, showing signs of use.</p> </blockquote> <p>oh no D:</p> <blockquote> <p>too much space between atoms, amazon prime impossible</p> </blockquote> <p>I have learned something valuable.</p> 
