					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8765194#post-4119352</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8765194/scp-4348#post-4119352</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 15 Jan 2019 02:25:58 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mark Penrice</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1858819</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Aw. I'm kinda sad, really, even though the notebook suggests it was for the best.</p> <p>Given his meddling with brain-twisting retrocausal continuity weirdness, was he still able to get the startup loan from Bank Of Pluto in a normal fashion or did that also include messing about with the timeline?</p> <p>Interesting look behind the scenes to show there's both hard work and surprisingly hard science behind everything, despite the pidgin English and garish Comic Sans adverts (which tbh I'd classify as the most anomalous part of the whole deal).</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
